m/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/18163413/LTG_CURL_OutdoorFishing_22-632x420.jpg 632w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/18163413/LTG_CURL_OutdoorFishing_22.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/18163413/LTG_CURL_OutdoorFishing_22.jpg 2000w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/18163413/LTG_CURL_OutdoorFishing_22-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/18163413/LTG_CURL_OutdoorFishing_22-800x532.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/18163413/LTG_CURL_OutdoorFishing_22-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/18163413/LTG_CURL_OutdoorFishing_22-768x511.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/18163413/LTG_CURL_OutdoorFishing_22-1536x1021.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/18163413/LTG_CURL_OutdoorFishing_22-696x463.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/18163413/LTG_CURL_OutdoorFishing_22-1068x710.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/18163413/LTG_CURL_OutdoorFishing_22-1920x1277.jpg 1920w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/18163413/LTG_CURL_OutdoorFishing_22-632x420.jpg 632w\"></a></h2><h2>Leatherman Curl Availability and Pricing</h2><p>The Curl ($80 MSRP), Rachet Driver adapter ($30 MSRP), and Bit Kit ($25 MSRP) are available through Leatherman’s <a href=\"https://www.leatherman.com/home\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">website</a>. As with all Leatherman products, each is backed by a 100% satisfaction guarantee and a 25-year warranty.</p></div></div>","author":"Jilli Cluff","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"bb4e1f515165ff31c03447ce5b5e8e181644286fa0f03e126ff45e1440e79e94","category":"Cycling"}